## Detection

### `POST /detect/`

Run the full 7-step detection pipeline.

**Request**
```json
{
  "platform": "YouTube",
  "username": "@creator",
  "caption": "Match highlights reel",
  "content_type": "sports",
  "scenario": "deepfake",
  "media_url": "https://..."
}
```

**Scenarios**: `normal`, `crop`, `blur`, `manipulated`, `deepfake`, `adversarial`, `news`, `entertainment`, `education`, `scam`, `insufficient`

**Response** (truncated)
```json
{
  "job_id": "uuid",
  "platform": "YouTube",
  "similarity": 0.52,
  "fingerprint_hash": "a3f1c2d4",
  "ml": { "label": "TAMPERED", "manipulation_probability": 0.89, "trust_score": 0.11 },
  "integrity": { "score": 0.28, "flags": ["Face landmark distortion", "Lip-sync mismatch"] },
  "trust": { "trust_score": 0.40, "risk_tier": "high_risk" },
  "ai_analysis": {
    "decision": "EMERGENCY_TAKEDOWN",
    "severity": "CRITICAL",
    "risk_label": "HIGH_RISK",
    "reasoning_points": ["92% face landmark — exceeds AI threshold", "..."],
    "dmca_needed": true,
    "source": "claude"
  },
  "case_id": "VM-A1B2C3D4",
  "processing_ms": 1420.5
}
```

### `GET /detect/stats`

```json
{ "total_scans": 42, "status": "operational" }
```

