## Enforcement

### `POST /enforce/dmca`

Generate a DMCA takedown notice via Claude AI.

**Request**
```json
{
  "case_id": "VM-A1B2C3D4",
  "platform": "YouTube",
  "username": "@infringer",
  "caption": "stolen content",
  "content_type": "sports",
  "analysis": {
    "similarity": 0.82,
    "integrity_score": 0.25,
    "ml_label": "TAMPERED",
    "ml_confidence": 0.91,
    "decision": "TAKEDOWN",
    "severity": "HIGH"
  }
}
```

**Response**
```json
{
  "case_id": "VM-A1B2C3D4",
  "subject": "DMCA Copyright Infringement Notice — Case VM-A1B2C3D4",
  "body": "Dear YouTube Trust & Safety Team...",
  "evidence_summary": "...",
  "action_recommendation": "1. Submit...",
  "source": "claude"
}
```

