## Cases

### `GET /cases/`

List enforcement cases (newest first).

Query params: `limit` (default 50), `offset` (default 0)

### `PATCH /cases/{case_id}`

```json
{ "status": "dmca_filed", "notes": "Submitted to YouTube legal" }
```

Status values: `open`, `under_review`, `dmca_filed`, `resolved`, `closed`

